Merge pull request #110 from sschuberth/master

Make unit tests pass on Windows

Make unit tests pass on Windows

The SdkResolver was always initialized for non-Windows, resulting in
backslashes in paths not being correctly escaped when writing them to
local.properties. Fix that by using the real platform the tests run on.

Merge pull request #107 from Alexander--/patch-1

Do not proceed when configuration step has thrown

Do not proceed when configuration step has thrown

Do not attempt SDK resolution after exception has been thrown in evaluation phase. Otherwise, when `afterEvaluate` code fails (naturally, the evaluation was not completed!), the actual configuration exception gets swallowed without a trace.

Check for prior configuration exception in `afterEvaluate`.

Merge pull request #39 from alexsydell/fix-play-services-support-dependency

Account for Play Services dependency on the support library.

Account for Play Services dependency on the support library.

Fixes #31 by making sure that the support library repository is present when
trying to resolve dependencies on Play Services, without which an exception was
thrown causing the plugin to think that Play Services was always outdated. Also
updates tests to reflect this dependency and fail without the fix.
